OL,5,EDEAR 'ZINE                S/--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,6,E                                       
OL,7,BPeople say they are animal lovers, yet 
OL,8,Bthey eat the things they say they love.
OL,9,B                                       
OL,10,BIf you ask them why this is so, like,  
OL,11,Bwould they eat a cat or a dolphin, they
OL,12,Bsay no, as if cows, sheep and chickens 
OL,13,Bare in some way different.             
OL,15,BWhy should this hypocritical human race
OL,16,Babuse its position in the circle of    
OL,17,Blife to make animals' lives a misery.  
OL,18,BHumans should be ashamed.              
OL,19,ESpace Vegan                            
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````4/5``
