OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BThis week we're continuing our pleas   
OL,8,Bfor your real-life stories to use on   
OL,9,Bour pages.                             
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,EThe subject is: X Files type psychic   
OL,12,Ephenomena.BHave you ever seen an alien?
OL,13,BChatted with an extra terrestrial      
OL,14,Bbeing? Ever been zoomed to another     
OL,15,Bdimension? However odd, write in.      
OL,17,BTell us about your experiences, whether
OL,18,Bfunny or freaky. We're waiting to hear 
OL,19,Ball about it.                          
